{
  "stem": "19837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we couldn't-- of course it went a little-- gradually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't go into parks anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't sit on the bench in a public park, couldn't go to theaters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So to begin with, every-- especially the older people, like my parents, they thought it will go by.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we formed our own cultural events, as operas and-- not in big opera houses or what, but we did our own cultural things, because we were used to going to the theater, movies, and operas.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you recall your first-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the first time you noticed the Nazi power affecting your life?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that came, actually, overnight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rapidly, rapidly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a private Hebrew teacher with me started talking conversational Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember the story I read.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I looked out the window, and we heard these terrible songs and saw them marching.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, oh, what is that now?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's really--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Nazis in the brown uniforms, and the SS, which was worse, was in the black uniforms with the black boots.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was also-- everything, '33 and '34.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hilde.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my sister got married in '33, and my father bought my brother-in-law and her a store, a Jewish were-- owners-- the owners were Jewish and left Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to my father, why do you buy them a store?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These Jewish people, they left, and what do you think Hilde and her husband will have to do?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, don't talk that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He will go by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had other bad people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They go down, and-- and we will stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they had a good business, but it didn't make any sense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These people had a reason to leave, the Jewish people who owned the store.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
